OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778497376
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus ship being sent
OL,4,Cto North West hospital
OL,6,FBritish passengers and staff on the
OL,7,Fcruise ship at the centre of the
OL,8,Fhantavirus outbreak will be taken to a
OL,9,Fhospital in the north west to isolate
OL,10,Fwhen they return to the UK.
OL,12,FIt is understood that British people
OL,13,Ffrom the ship will be transferred to
OL,14,FArrowe Park on the Wirral.
OL,16,FThe hospital was previously used for
OL,17,Fpeople returning from China at the
OL,18,Fstart of the Covid-19 pandemic in
OL,19,Fearly 2020, after being flown back to
OL,20,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
