PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778497376
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus ship being sent
OL,4,Cto North West hospital
OL,6,FAn email from the chief executive for
OL,7,FWirral University Teaching Hospital
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust said the hospital
OL,9,F"will be welcoming guests on Sunday 10
OL,10,FMay".
OL,12,FJanelle Holmes said: "Nobody showing
OL,13,Fany symptoms will be transferred here.
OL,15,F"If anyone becomes unwell after
OL,16,Farrival, they will be transferred
OL,17,Fquickly to another facility."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
