PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778497376
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus ship being sent
OL,4,Cto North West hospital
OL,6,FThree people have died after the
OL,7,Foutbreak of the virus on the MV
OL,8,FHondius vessel which is expected to
OL,9,Fdock in Tenerife on Sunday, 10 May.
OL,11,FOfficials from the UK Health Security
OL,12,FAgency (UKHSA) and Foreign Office said
OL,13,FBritons will be tested for hantavirus
OL,14,Fbefore they disembark the cruise ship.
OL,16,FIf people test negative and are not
OL,17,Fdisplaying symptoms, they will be
OL,18,Ftaken straight to a dedicated
OL,19,Frepatriation flight staffed by medical
OL,20,Fprofessionals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
