FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778497376
OL,3,CBritons on hantavirus ship being sent
OL,4,Cto North West hospital
OL,6,FA UKHSA spokesperson said the risk "to
OL,7,Fgeneral public remains very low".
OL,9,FThe World Health Organisation said
OL,10,Fthere had been six confirmed
OL,11,Fhantavirus cases linked to the MV
OL,12,FHondius ship and that four patients
OL,13,Fwere currently in hospital.
OL,15,FIt added that a total of eight cases,
OL,16,Fincluding three deaths, had been
OL,17,Freported ` with one suspected case
OL,18,Fbeing reclassified after testing
OL,19,Fnegative for hantavirus.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
